<HEADLINE>
NO. 7 SHOULDN'T TRY FOR NO. 3
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TOM HOFFARTH  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ John Elway , you've just won the MVP award and
your second straight Super Bowl championship, crushed the dreams of
your former coach and kept millions from witnessing ``The Dirty
Bird'' on national television . . . now what are you going to do?
</P>
<P>
   Collect your thoughts. Then collect your belongings.
</P>
<P>
   Escape the rush one last time. Quit tempting fate.
</P>
<P>
   Take the kids to Disney World (check the safety records first).
And don't come back for a long, (begin ital)lonn
</P>
</TEXT>
