<HEADLINE>
THIS JUST IN...THE BIMBO ERA IS OVER  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This 900-word ``separate buy'' article is from The Independent
newspaper in London.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
  
