<SLUG> BC-GRAVITY-INTERNET-STOCKS-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
`FLYING BLIND' INTERNET SHARES WILL SOON CRASH  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This excellent ``separate buy'' article is from the current (week
beginning 30 January 1999) Economist magazine.)  
  
