<HEADLINE>
POPE JOHN PAUL GEORGE RINGO II: THE MAGICAL MYSTIC TOUR  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This excellent 450-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 30 January 1999) Economist magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
