<P>
   &UR; ATTENTION EDITORS: &LR;  The following is the budget for Rodale's
Healthy Living stories for release the week of Mon., Feb. 8.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ATTENTION EDITORS: Four stories will be transmitted today. The
other two will move tomorrow morning. The art will posted on
Newscom and transmitted via e-mail tomorrow as well. We apologize
for the delay. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   These articles are free to Rodale Healthy Living clients. They
can be purchased individually by non-clients. To purchase a story
or for information on how to subscribe to Rodale's Healthy Living,
call (888) 269-8796.
</P>
<P>
   Photos are available on Wieck, Newscom or through e-mail.
</P>
<P>
   1. STROKE: A HEALTHY BRAIN DIET. From ``New Foods for Healing''
with art. The factors that can cause stroke are ones you can
prevent by choosing the right foods. Here, a guide.(slugged:
BC-RODALE-COVER-NYTSF).
</P>
<P>
   2. HEALTH BRIEFS. From Prevention and Runner's World with art.
Breathe away your hot flashes; chase away scary dreams; five steps
to beat the heat of hot flashes; new foods for health. (slugged:
BC-RODALE-BRIEFS-NYTSF).
</P>
<P>
