   MOMA-PS1 (New York) _ The Museum of Modern Art and P.S.1
announce plans to merge. By Carol Vogel.
</P>
<P>
   BRITAIN-VICTORIA-MUSEAUM (London) _ The Victoria and Albert
Museum struggles for attention and funds. By Alan Riding.
</P>
<P>
   FILM-CAMEOS (Undated) _ Fleeting fame on screen, as cameo film
appearances multiply. By Peter Applebome.
</P>
<P>
   TV-NOTEBOOK (Undate) _ A Critic's Notebook on ``Spin City'' and
``Seinfeld.'' By Walter Goodman.
</P>
<P>
