children's books are announced.
</P>
<P>
   SAINTS-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Prepare for Saints,'' by Steven
Watson (Random House). Reviewed by Michiko Kakutani.
</P>
<P>
   TV-AIDS-REVIEW (Undated) _ On PBS's Nova: ``Surviving AIDS.''
Reviewed by Walter Goodman.
</P>
