operator of a far-flung restaurant chain whose holdings include
chicken, Mexican and hamburger speciality stores, said Monday that
its stock will be delisted by NASDAQ regulators. The company
operates Koo Koo Roo, Hamburger Hamlet and El Torito. By Gregory J.
Wilcox.
