<P>
   BURLESON, Texas _ Brittany Williams has taken Girl Scout cookie
sales into a new neighborhood: cyberspace. The 7-year-old Brownie
has taken to the Internet to sell those celebrated thin mints and
other popular Girl Scout cookies. Although Brittany doesn't prefer
one method over another, she says, ``It's better than having to go
door to door when it's cold or hot.'' By CATHERINE S. DAILEY. Story
has moved in ``a'' general news category. &QL; 
