BKO-RAFAEL (Los Angeles) _ Feature on Simi Valley High School's
Rafael Berumen, the second-best basketball player in the region. He
has committed to New Mexico and already is a big star there among
Mexican-Americans, who beseiged him with autograph requests during
a recent visit. 
