   IMPEACHMENT-JORDAN (Washington) _ Presidential confidant Vernon
Jordan goes before House prosecutors and White House lawyers in a
closed-door deposition Tuesday. We review what Jordan has told the
grand jury about his job search for Monica Lewinsky and what the
lawyers on each side are hoping to coax out of him. By DAN
