SCHEDULE FOR DEPOSITIONS IN CLINTON TRIAL 
</HEADLINE>
  (See also IMPEACH, IMPEACH-JORDAN, IMPEACH-LEWINSKY,
IMPEACH-STARR-LEAKS) 
(lb) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
